SnowballStemmer - class stemmer.SnowballStemmer.
Title: SnowballStemmer.java
Description: This class is a wrapper for the Snowball stemmers (see ) for
  • danish,
  • dutch,
  • english,
  • finnish,
  • french,
  • german,
  • italian,
  • norwegian,
  • portuguese,
  • russian,
  • spanish,
  • swedish. It takes string value form the annotationFeature of annotationType in annotationSetName, stems it and adds new feture "stem" into the same annotation Type.
